     SHORT="Ncurses based file manager with vi like keybindings"

cat << EOF
Vifm is an ncurses based file manager with vi like keybindings/modes/options/
commands/configuration, which also borrows some useful ideas from mutt.
Vifm gives you complete keyboard control over your files without having to learn
a new set of commands.
EOF
